ff jewelry and personal belongings since then she has dedicated herself to animal welfare issues and has made countless donations to the cause including  for a mass sterilization and adoption program for bucharest’s stray dogs copyright   look to the stars please share this page share on facebook share on twitter share on google share on reddit share by email share on pinterest profiles celebrities brigitte bardot charities brigitte bardot foundation causes animals please enable javascript to view the comments powered by disqus comments powered by disqus related news stories the hsus announces st annual genesis award winners apr   netflix’s “the ivory game” rolling stone’s “the dog factory” and chicago tribune’s “the price of pork” head the lineup of  winners of the st annual genesis awards presented by the humane society of the united states more → brigitte bardot joins european animal groups to urge air france to stop transporting monkeys for research jan   pamela anderson appeals to french assembly to ban foie gras cruelty jan   martin sheen unveils newest vessel in sea shepherd fleet oct   latest news bryan cranston wraps up day two of his firstever uso tour jul   new york times bestselling author and awardwinning actor screenwriter director and producer bryan cranston visited with more than  service members and officially wrapped up day two of his firstever uso tour more → barbara sinatras charity legacy jul   kiehls th annual liferide for amfar jul   us adam clayton honored at musicares map fund benefit concert jul   more news → top celebrities elton john bill clinton annie lennox paul mccartney bono sting ellen degeneres george clooney thousands more celebrities → top charities unicef peta red cross elton john aids foundation makeawish foundation save the children thousands more charities → follow us on facebook top causes aids  hiv  animals  atriskdisadvantaged youths  cancer  children  education  environment  health  human rights  miscellaneous  poverty  wo