en beret michael mantenuto took his own life man  who raped a girl  with an iq of  is sentenced to just six months in prison lesbian girlfriend of yearold killed by her sister in california car crash live streamed on instagram blames social media and not the intoxicated sibling laptops tablets and all electronics larger than a cellphone are now subjected to extra security measures for all passengers at us airports man  who kidnapped and raped a fouryearold girl and left her with an incurable std is due for sentencing and could get a life term steve jobs widow and her boyfriend holiday in croatia on the million yacht the late apple founder built but never got to use… as his daughter tucks an iphone into her waistband she wanted to sack me because i looked too beautiful bridesmaids reveal the terrifying demands made upon them by bridezillas  including a pregnancy ban and removing tattoos amazon plans to hire  people in one week with massive job fair in which candidates across  states will be offered jobs on the spot tragedy as threeyearold autistic twin boys drown in their familys backyard pool after sneaking out of the house man  arrested after drunkenly walking around maine town wearing a clown mask and brandishing a machete which was taped to his amputated arm exclusive sumner redstones ex sydney holland  secretly puts home up for sale in a bid to join real housewives of beverly hills and shed gold digger reputation what not to say in the office if you want to be respected the most infuriating workplace jargon revealed – including ‘touch base’ and ‘blue sky thinking’  go commando have a safe threesome and shave each other how to take your sex life from dull to daring without going the full fifty shades or feeling like a complete idiot oj simpson will go back to prison says exmanager who reveals a number of people have scores to settle with the juice and are out for revenge girl  cured of lifethreatening rare disease after receiving a kidney from her yearold grandmo